+# Word Garden
+
+> Word Garden is a small TUI game designed as a more cheerful alternative to
+> Hangman. It is intended as a slightly more adventurous "Hello World" project
+> for testing AI-assisted software development. The game includes input
+> validation, state management, a simple loop, win/loss conditions, and a
+> friendly terminal interface.
+
+Guess the hidden word one letter at a time. Correct guesses help your garden
+grow; wrong guesses cost a unit of water and let a weed appear. Reveal the
+whole word before the water runs out and your garden blooms.
+
+## Requirements
+
+- Python 3.11 or newer
+- Standard library only (no third-party packages)
+
+## How to run
+
+From the project root:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden
+```
+
+Options:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty easy     # easy | normal | hard
+python3 -m word_garden --ascii               # plain ASCII visuals (no emoji)
+```
+
+- `--difficulty` chooses the starting water and the pool of word lengths:
+
+  | Difficulty | Water | Word length |
+  |---|---:|---:|
+  | easy   | 8 | 4–6 letters |
+  | normal | 6 | 5–8 letters |
+  | hard   | 4 | 7+ letters  |
+
+- `--ascii` swaps the emoji visuals for plain-text symbols, useful in
+  terminals that do not render emoji.
+
+## Rules
+
+- A random secret word is chosen and shown as blanks.
+- Enter a single letter per turn (case and surrounding spaces don't matter).
+- A correct letter is revealed in every position it appears.
+- A wrong letter costs one unit of water and adds a weed.
+- Guessing a letter you already tried, or any invalid input (empty, multiple
+  characters, numbers, symbols), does not cost water.
+- You **win** when the whole word is revealed.
+- You **lose** when the water reaches zero before the word is revealed.
+
+Press Ctrl-C or Ctrl-D at any time to leave the garden; the game exits
+cleanly with a friendly goodbye.
+
+## Sample screen
+
+```text
+🌱 Word Garden
+
+Garden: 🌿  The garden is growing nicely.
+
+Word:     G _ R _ E _
+Guessed:  A E G R
+Water:  4/6  💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:  2/6  🌿🌿
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Guess a letter:
+```
+
+In `--ascii` mode the same screen uses plain symbols:
+
+```text
+* Word Garden *
+
+Garden: *  The garden is growing nicely.
+
+Word:     G _ R _ E _
+Guessed:  A E G R
+Water:  4/6  ****
+Weeds:  2/6  --
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Guess a letter:
+```
+
+Enjoy tending your word garden!
